# Anonymous sub
topic read $SYS/#
topic read builders/#
topic read events/#
topic read jobs/#
topic read tasks/+
topic read cancel/#

# Builder pub/sub - copy for each builder
user arch_name
topic readwrite builders/arch/name
topic read events/#
topic read jobs/arch/name/+
topic readwrite tasks/+
topic read cancel/#

# IRC pub/sub
user irc
topic read builders/#
topic read events/#
topic read jobs/#
topic read tasks/+
topic readwrite cancel/#

# enqueue pub/sub
user enqueue
topic read builders/#
topic readwrite events/#
topic readwrite jobs/#
topic readwrite tasks/+
topic readwrite cancel/#

# All clients
pattern write $SYS/broker/connection/%c/state
